                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- A prayer to be recited after a Synaxarion reading in <locus target="#116ra">116ra</locus>: ዘአቅረብኩ᎓ ማኅሌተ᎓ አዘኪርየ᎓ አዕላፈ᎓ እምእለ᎓ ተጸምዱከ᎓
                        ዘልፈ…</note>
                     <note>This prayer is often recited after Synaxarion readings; it is usually
                        included at the end of a Ms., cp. Mss.<ref type="mss" corresp="ESdd037">DD-037</ref>,<ref type="mss" corresp="ESfbm007">FBM-007</ref>,<ref type="mss" corresp="ESmr041">MR-041</ref>,<ref type="mss" corresp="ESfbm007">FBM-007</ref>,<ref type="mss" corresp="ESum005">UM-005</ref>,<ref type="mss" corresp="ESsm007">SM-007</ref>,<ref type="mss" corresp="ESmsm005">MSM-005</ref>,<ref type="mss" corresp="ESmsm008">MSM-008</ref>.</note>
                  </msItem>
